<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Animal Adoption</title>
    <link href="../CSS/adoptions.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body  style="background-color:#d5bc93">
    <header>
        <div class="navbar">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="nav-logo">
                </div>
                <a href="../" style="text-decoration:none; color:white;">ANIMAL ALLIES</a>
            </div> 

           <div class="tabs">
                    <div class="home tab-style">
                        <a href="../">Home</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="our_gallery tab-style">
                        <a href="../our_gallery">Our Gallery</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="adoptions tab-style">
                        <a  href="../animals">adoptions</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="membership tab-style">
                        <a  href="../membership">Membership</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="donation tab-style">
                        <a  href="../donation"> donation </a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="about_us tab-style">
                        <a href="../About_Us">About Us</a>
                    </div>
           </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="content-helpline" style="text-align:center; background-color:#5d4529; height:40px; display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center; font-size:1rem; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:white; border-radius:5px"  >Adoption-Helpline: 999 999 999
        </div>
        <div class="content-heading" style="padding:20px; font-family:'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; color:#5d4529; ">
            <h1>Animals For Adoption</h1>
        </div>
        <form method="GET" action="/animals" id="form">
            <div class="gender"style="display:inline-block; padding:20px">
                <p style="font-size:1rem; font-family:sans-serif; font-weight:500;">Gender</p>
                <select name="gender" id="genderFilter">
                    <option value="All" <%= gender === 'All' ? 'selected' : '' %>>All</option>
                    <option value="Male" <%= gender === 'Male' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Male</option>
                    <option value="Female" <%= gender === 'Female' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Female</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="age-group"style="display:inline-block; padding:20px">
                <p style="font-size:1rem; font-family:sans-serif; font-weight:500;">Age Group</p>
                <select style="height:40px; width:400px; border-radius:10px " name="ageFilter">
                    <option value="all" <%= ageRange === 'all' ? 'selected' : '' %>>All</option>
                    <option value="under_9_months" <%= ageRange === 'under_9_months' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Baby (under 9 months)</option>
                    <option value="9_months_to_6_years" <%= ageRange === '9_months_to_6_years' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Adult (1-6 years)</option>
                    <option value="6_years_plus" <%= ageRange === '6_years_plus' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Senior (6+ years)</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <button type="submit"  id="Modify">Apply Filters</button>
        </form>
        <div class="content-div">

            <% if (animals.length > 0) { %>
                <% animals.forEach(animal => { %>
    
            <a href="../animal_info/<%= animal.img %>" style="text-decoration:none; color:green;" >
                <div class="content-box">
                    <img src="../image?name=<%= animal.img %>" alt="animal.name" style=" height: 67%; width:100%;border-radius:10px;">
                    <p style="text-align:center; padding:10px; font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-size:20px; color:#009900;     font-weight:900;"><%= animal.name %></p>
                    <pre style="font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; text-align:center; padding:20px;">Gender: <%= animal.gender %>   <i class="fa-solid fa-circle" style="font-size:9px;"></i><%= animal.age < 9 ? 'Baby' : (animal.age <= 72 ? 'Adult' : 'Senior') %></pre>
                    <p style="text-align:center; font-weight:900 ; color:white; background-color:#009900; margin-top:10px;border-radius:10px;">A D O P T</p>
                </div>
            </a>
    
            <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <p>No animals found for the selected filters.</p>
        <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <div class="foot-panel">
           <div class="box1 foot-box" style="width:500px">
                <div class="foot-logo">
                    <img style="height: 80px;" src="../statics/logo.jpeg" alt="foot-logo">
                    <p>PEEPAL FARM</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box1-content">
                    <p>Animal welfare is not just about animals. It is about us. Our living conditions, our children, our earth. Cruelty to animals has a significant and irreversible impact on peaceful societies, human health, the economy, and the environment</p>
                </div>
           </div> 
           <div class="box2 foot-box">
            <h2>Quick Links</h2>
            <ul style="list-style-type:none" >
                <li><a href="../">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="../our_gallery">Our Gallery</a></li>
                <li><a  href="../animals">adoptions</a></li>
                <li> <a  href="../membership">Membership</a></li>
                <li><a  href="../donation"> donation </a></li>
                <li><a href="../About_Us">About Us</a></li>
            </ul>
            
           </div>
           <div class="box3 foot-box">
                    <h2>Follow Us On</h2>
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/peepalfarm/?hl=en"  target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i></a> 
                   <a href="https://www.youtube.com/peepalfarm"  target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i></a>
                   <a href="https://www.whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va25pme23n3YaavT6a3u"  target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp"></i></a>
                   <a href="https://t.me/s/peepalfarm"  target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-telegram"></i></a>
                    <h2 class="heading2">Find Us</h2>
                    <p>HQ: People For Animals, 14 Ashoka Road, Jantar Mantar Road, New Delhi 110001.</p>
           </div>
        </div>
   </footer>
</body>
</html>